definitions.text:
@khem
- Keep a post-natal diet (with abstinence from some kinds of food believed to be unsuitable to women just out of childbirth)
=ăn khem+To be on a post-natal diet

@khen thưởng
- Commend and reward
=Khen thưởng những sáng kiến của công nhân+To commend and reward the innovations of workers

@kheo khư
- Thin and weak
=ốm mãi trông kheo khư lắm+To look quite thin and weak after a long illness

@khe khắt
* adj
- austere; severe

@khen ngợi
* verb
- to command, to praise
